subject: Attention:Beneficiary.
body:
Attention:Beneficiary.
In order to improve on your fund transfer constraints and delay, your outstanding payment is due for payment from our United States Government approved direct paying institution.
We have successfully deposited your $9,7 Million USD with the Federal Reserve Payment System for an accessible, safe, and efficient completion of your fund transfer to your nominated bank.
Kindly reverse back to us for further advice and instruction with contact details of Federal Reserve Payment System link and office to contact for your payment processing.
Contact Mr. Tom Frank.
Email: 
ftom13866@gmail.com
Sincerely,
Jennifer Burns.

subject: Re:   Attention:Beneficiary.
body:
Hello Jennifer Burns,

Thank you so much for your message. It's really exciting to hear about this fund transfer! I'm just a bit confused about the process, could you please explain it a bit more? How does the Federal Reserve Payment System work exactly? And how did my Million USD end up there?

Also, you mentioned Mr. Tom Frank. Could you tell me more about his role in this process? Is he someone I should be contacting directly?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
John
